narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes. I would highly recommend this course to another student for all of the reasons listed above. This course has really opened my eyes to such an important field of study that will affect all of our futures.

Completely recommend. Such a unique classroom style and classroom topic! This class gives you a new perspective on the way religions influence human relationships with the environment and is so incredibly fascinating.
